I'm not the same
frightened boy you threw in a cell.

87
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:59,033
No treatments, no therapy.

88
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,599
Just some ice baths

89
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:04,719
and some...
Electric shocks once in a while.

90
