You're not listening to me, Warden!

101
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:41,273
Jonathan Crane is no more.

102
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,437
Call me by my true name.

103
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,277
The Scarecrow.

104
