Stop.

135
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,599
Brothers and sisters, look at you.

136
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:17,875
Prisoners, all of you.

137
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:20,351
My father would have freed you.

138
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:23,113
But he was killed.

139
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:26,193
Murdered by the GCPD.

140
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:28,352
Men who couldn't understand.

141
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,640
But they will.

142
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,756
For you will be my army.

143
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,080
(ALL SCREAMING)

144
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:39,474
And those men who killed my father

145
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:42,996
shall truly know fear.

146
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,440
(SCREAMING)

147
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,229
James Gordon.

148
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:01,271
James Gordon?

149
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,120
There you are.

150
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,960
Play nice.

151
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:09,680
No.

152
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:15,640
I see you've caught one of them.
What about the other fellow?

153
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,397
I have no idea who you're talking about.

154
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,640
Jonathan Crane?

155
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:24,233
People share with me because they
trust me to get things done.

156
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,880
Unlike you.

157
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:31,117
S0 this boy who created this
lethal toxin which almost killed me,

158
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,349
where is he?

159
