Whereabouts unknown for now.

160
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,509
Why am I not surprised?

161
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,195
I mean, really.

162
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:42,159
The only thing the GCPD
knows how to do well is fail.

163
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:46,751
What is a penguin? A bird or a mammal?

164
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,911
Bird. It is a bird.

165
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,560
Like a chicken?

166
00:09:56,720 --> 00:10:00,793
Time and time again. the GCPD expose
themselves for what they truly are.

167
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:04,791
An outdated, ineffectual.
And corrupt institution.

168
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:09,515
How much longer must our citizens
suffer their incompetence?

169
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:12,035
This coming from a man
who takes money from criminals

170
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:15,397
in exchange for a license allowing them
to victimize innocent people.

171
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,709
And it is working.

172
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:23,996
Jim, why can't you see that I am not
here to destroy your beloved GCPD,

173
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,555
but to save it?

174
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:28,350
And through that, Gotham.

175
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,400
Your licenses are illegal,

176
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,994
and I will arrest anyone I find
who is issued one.

177
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:40,071
S0 sure your Boy Scout morality
can protect this city, Jim?

178
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:43,633
How well has that worked in the past?

179
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:47,835
Should I list the victims of
your antiquated righteousness?

180
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,832
Instead. let me make you a deal.

181
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:54,835
Find this Jonathan Crane
and lock him up within 24 hours

182
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:57,829
or admit to me, your subordinates.

183
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,389
And the people of Gotham

184
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,194
that you failed.

185
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:04,349
And allow me to clean this city up!

186
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,075
Good for you, Jim.

187
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:15,840
- (Game on.
- UNDISTINCT CHATTER)

188
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:28,800
What are you doing here?

189
