Have I taught you nothing?

190
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:35,756
I could've slit your throat
before you even <i>saw</i> me.

191
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,239
I found this on the door this morning.

192
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:47,672
Someone left this inside last night.

193
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,519
Thank you for coming, ladies.

194
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:17,915
No way.

195
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,000
I saw you die.

196
