That so?

197
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,120
It is Gotham.

198
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,876
- Check for a pulse next time.
- I will.

199
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,319
Right after I slit your throat.

200
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:31,916
So what happened to you?

201
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,000
Long story.

202
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:38,192
Right now, all you need to know
is that I'm back.

203
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,354
And like the card says.

204
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:44,031
An opportunity awaits you.

205
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,640
A new beginning.

206
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,593
You sure you wanna get this close?

207
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,200
Please hear me out.

208
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,800
Not a day goes by
where I don't think about what I did.

209
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:57,956
If I could take it back,
trust me, I would.

210
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,639
I wouldn't mind a do-over myself.

211
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:04,558
Perhaps I'II finish the job this time.

212
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:07,760
I was jealous.

213
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,155
I was stupid.

214
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:12,153
I am sorry.

215
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,952
Kill me if you don't believe me.

216
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:26,750
S0 is this your place now?

217
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,753
This is our place.

218
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,400
Another club?

219
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:33,800
In Gotham?

220
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,640
How original.

221
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,115
It's not a club.

222
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,120
Penguin's taking over.

223
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:08,876
Like it or not,
every criminal in this city

224
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:12,914
is gonna go to him for a license
to mug. steal, or blow stuff up.

225
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:18,154
Those criminals are gonna need supplies,
and that is where we come in.

226
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:22,435
Not only will we be able to facilitate
these lowlifes,

227
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:25,319
but we'II also find out
what they're planning

228
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:26,674
and how it's going down.

229
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:32,234
But I will not go forward
without you both.

230
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:36,512
This is our way back on top.

231
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,240
No.

232
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,709
What you took from me,

233
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:44,751
I will never be able to get back.

234
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:48,839
Just feel lucky I don't burn this place
to the ground.

235
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,320
(nooa CLOSES)

236
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:56,757
This will be good for all of us.

237
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:58,953
Please talk to her.

238
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,159
I don't wanna hear it, Alfred.

239
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,435
I'm going back out there.

240
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:20,312
I'm not gonna let this trail go cold.

241
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:23,191
Farbe it from me
to stop you, Master Bruce.

242
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:30,840
You're not coming?

243
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,440
No, sir.

244
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:34,560
And why not?

245
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:41,396
Because, as last night proved,
you are simply not ready.

246
00:15:42,040 --> 00:15:43,736
Yeah, you can chuck a punch.
You can block one.

247
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:45,637
You're quick on your toes.
I'Il give you that.

248
00:15:46,640 --> 00:15:48,870
What if they've got guns, Master Bruce?

249
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:53,400
Out there,

250
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:56,594
Alfred, I feel more alive
than I've ever felt before.

251
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:00,715
Do you understand that?

252
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:07,590
And that is precisely why
I am not stopping you, sir.

253
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:09,915
But you'll excuse me

254
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,310
if I don't wanna stand by
and watch you get shot.

255
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,200
Hey.

256
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:27,511
Mental asylum's under siege.
The lunatics are running riot.

257
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,955
The guards called it in
before they bolted for the hills.

258
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:31,951
- Crane?
- He made more toxins, right?

259
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:34,395
What happens when you dose 100 nutjobs?

260
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:35,480
AII right, listen up!

261
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,474
There's a riot at the asylum.

262
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:39,432
I need as many of you as can come.

263
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:41,119
Who's with me?

264
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,320
Good luck with that.

